<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PersonNote/2422> rdfs:label "Person Note: #2422" ;
	a dprr:PersonNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Honored as a patron at Magnesia on the Maeander (L Magn. 143), and at Caunus along with his brother Aulus (G. E. Bean, JHS 74, 1954, 90, no. 26-AEpig. 1957, 165). Probably sons of the consul of 60, but not specifically termed magistrates or senators: See Wiseman, NM 210, no. 9." .
